---
/*
  Vintage botanical rose illustrations — the brand's core visual signature.
  Rendered as layered inline SVG, positioned at section corners and bleeding
  off-frame. Decorative only (aria-hidden, pointer-events:none).

  variant:
    hero-tl / hero-br      large blush rose for hero corners
    testimonial            single bloom, top-left, 0.75 opacity
    taste-tl / taste-br    pale cream roses for the dark terracotta CTA band
*/
